      <abstract>
        <t>&lt;p&gt;This document specifies a stable naming scheme for the nameservers that serve the zones IN-ADDR.ARPA and IP6.ARPA in the DNS.  These zones contain data that facilitate reverse mapping (address to name).  This memo documents an Internet Best Current Practice.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
